text: Abacab is the eleventh studio album by Genesis. The album was released on September 24, 1981 through Atlantic Records. ==Track listing== All music written by Tony Banks, Phil Collins, and Mike Rutherford, except where noted. All songs arranged and performed by Genesis. Lyricists specified below.Giammetti, Mario (2021). Genesis 1975 to 2021 - The Phil Collins Years.
